73
00:03:24,495 --> 00:03:26,550
Moving on to Key Takeaways.

74
00:03:26,550 --> 00:03:31,141
Follow a structured approach - Requirements → Scale → Design → Deep Dive.

75
00:03:31,141 --> 00:03:36,322
Know the building blocks - Load balancers, caches, queues, databases.

76
00:03:36,322 --> 00:03:44,038
Understand trade-offs - Every decision has pros and cons. Practice estimation - Back-of-envelope math is crucial.

77
00:03:44,038 --> 00:03:47,355
Think about failures - How does the system handle failures?.

78
00:03:47,355 --> 00:03:51,598
Consider operations - Monitoring, deployment, maintenance.

79
00:03:51,598 --> 00:03:53,197
