80
00:03:53,197 --> 00:03:59,158
System design interviews test your ability to think at scale and make sound architectural decisions.

81
00:03:59,158 --> 00:04:05,865
Practice with real-world problems, understand the core concepts, and always communicate your thought process.

82
00:04:05,865 --> 00:04:10,685
The goal isn't a perfect design—it's demonstrating systematic problem-solving.

